The Summer Breeze Mates Bookcase Bed Collection combines handy storage with enchanting style. Featuring three generous-sized drawers for convenient under-bed storage, the sturdy bed is constructed of wood composite with a smooth laminate finish in a vanilla cream tone. Adding even more value are the optional nightstand and chest, allowing you to complete the collection in one easy checkout.

About South Shore Furniture A recognized leader in North American furniture and décor, South Shore Industries was established in 1940 and has been making furniture for three generations. Employing a team of over 900 employees in three factories in North America, their designs have earned a reputation for quality and excellence at affordable prices for today's family.

But at South Shore, furniture and décor items are only a part of so much more that’s meant to achieve the company's real goal: helping customers create a décor that’s a reflection of them. The folks at South Shore firmly believe that their role goes much further than the buying process. They want to help their customers every step of the way, from the initial research for home projects to repurposing décor years later to support, inspire, and even surprise customers with unique South Shore ideas. They have a passion for the furniture they design - a passion that includes a touch of genius and a dash of zany to every one of their creations. And this passion is what South Shore wants to share with their customers.
